ies is\nstrongly suppressed with respect to the \\LambdaCDM spectrum, particularly at\nsmall angular scales l\\gtrsim100.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Feb 2009 17:47:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2009 16:43:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-02"}
