30+/-45 km/s. We show that the close\ncompanion to the beta Cep primary is a valid classical Be star. It has a\nspectral type of B5Ve and is a relatively fast rotator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Feb 2009 12:52:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 1 Mar 2009 14:27:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
